==用途==
聖皮瑞旗經常裝飾在汽車保險槓上，並且亦飄揚在{{link-en|康瓦爾郡議會|Cornwall Council}}大廈等建築的上空<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cornishstudies.com/index.php?q=node/10 |title=How far has the “Cornish Revival” affected modern Cornwall? |access-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008211307/http://www.cornishstudies.com/index.php?q=node%2F10 |archive-date=2011-10-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。聖皮瑞旗亦在{{link-en|聖皮瑞節|St Piran's Day}}等康瓦爾本地的節日，以及{{link-en|康瓦爾橄欖球聯盟|Rugby union in Cornwall}}的比賽展示。聖皮瑞旗亦在全世界被用作康瓦爾僑民的象徵。許多機構和康瓦爾本地的企業亦在標誌中含有聖皮瑞旗的設計，例如[[循道宗|循道宗]]的康瓦爾教區。

在2012年6月的{{link-en|泰晤士鑽禧慶典|Thames Diamond Jubilee Pageant}}上，聖皮瑞旗和[[英格蘭國旗|英格蘭國旗]]、[[蘇格蘭國旗|蘇格蘭國旗]]、[[圣帕特里克十字|北愛爾蘭旗幟]]、[[倫敦市旗|倫敦市旗]]一同飄揚在{{link-en|皇家賽艇|Gloriana (barge)}}上<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.falmouthpacket.co.uk/news/westcornwall/9745015.St_Ives_lugger_flies_the_flag_at_Jubilee_river_pageant/?ref=rss|title=St Ives lugger flies the flag at Jubilee river pageant|publisher=Falmouth Packet|date=2012-06-06|access-date=2012-06-07|archive-date=2019-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190101002848/https://www.falmouthpacket.co.uk/news/westcornwall/9745015.St_Ives_lugger_flies_the_flag_at_Jubilee_river_pageant/?ref=rss|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Western Morning News">{{Cite web|url=http://www.thisiscornwall.co.uk/Mystery-Cornish-flag-jubilee-boat-solved/story-16366581-detail/story.html%23axzz2SOsN9zU9|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130505071742/http://www.thisiscornwall.co.uk/Mystery-Cornish-flag-jubilee-boat-solved/story-16366581-detail/story.html%23axzz2SOsN9zU9|archive-date=2013-05-05|title=Mystery over Cornish flag on jubilee boat is solved | This is Cornwall|access-date=2021-05-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

